Test Case: ID	2_01
	
Test Name:	testerzy.pl search functionality
	
Test Objective:	This test case is to verify if it is possible to display and hide the search field and if correct search results are displayed after performing a simple search.
	
High-level steps:	
"1. Navigate to testerzy.pl.
2. Locate the search icon and check that the search field is displayed.
3. Hide the search field.
4. Perform a simple search.
5. Check if correct search results are displayed."
	
Preconditions:	N/A
	
Additional information:	this test case should be performed on Windows, macOS
